cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper deals with improving the accuracy of neural network classifiers, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper specifically focuses on improving the performance of Softmax, a commonly used final layer in neural networks, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
